    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bags made of a porous material filled with a fine powder of charcoal, chalk, or pipe clay; used in pouncing.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
